<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GlideLineX Details</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css"> <!-- Link to your CSS file -->
</head>

<style>
  /* General Reset */
body, h1, h2, h3, p, a, button {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
}

body {
    background-color: #0a192f; /* Dark blue background */
    color: #ccd6f6; /* Light grey text */
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding: 20px;
}

.details-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: #112240; /* Slightly lighter blue for the container */
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #64ffda; /* Teal color for headings */
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-align: center;
}

p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}

strong {
    color: #64ffda; /* Teal color for strong text */
}

.btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #0a192f;
    background-color: #64ffda;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
}

.btn:hover {
    background-color: #52d1b2; /* Darker teal on hover */
}

/* Additional styles for a tech theme */
.tech-background {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a192f, #112240);
}

.tech-border {
    border: 1px solid #64ffda;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.tech-highlight {
    color: #64ffda;
    font-weight: bold;
}

/* Responsive Design */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .details-container {
        padding: 15px;
    }

    .btn {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
    }
}
</style>

<body>
    <div class="details-container">
        <h1>GlideLineX - National Level Line Follower Robot Competition</h1>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong> Showcase your robotic skills at GlideLineX, where precision meets speed! Build an autonomous robot that navigates a designated track, passes checkpoints, and overcomes challenges using your coding expertise.</p>
        <p><strong>Eligibility:</strong> Open to students across India.</p>
        <p><strong>Prize Pool:</strong> Exciting prizes for the winners!</p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> [Insert Date]</p>
        <p><strong>Location:</strong> [Insert Location]</p>
        <a href="https://forms.gle/9abxu3ejxiV1Dcus6" target="_blank">
            <button class="btn">Register Now</button>
        </a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>